cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Name: At the End of the Tunnel vol 3
cac:ProcurementProject.cbc:Description: A man is trapped in his own house after an accident confined him to a wheelchair. Since he is in debt, he decides to rent a room to an exotic dancer and her 6-year-old daughter. Their uncomfortable co-existence turns into friendship and sexual attraction, until he discovers that she is there for another reason; she and her associates believe they have organized the perfect crime.
